body_html:
Ugh, we have another cmakefile under contrib/android?
Adding @petewarden, as he is the owner of the android build.

In our CI, android builds are passing. ci.tensorflow.org is deprecated, and it has last ran the android build a month ago. So if you are referring to that one the results there are obsolete.
We are working to expose the new CIs results.

body:
Ugh, we have another cmakefile under contrib/android?
Adding @petewarden, as he is the owner of the android build.

In our CI, android builds are passing. ci.tensorflow.org is deprecated, and it has last ran the android build a month ago. So if you are referring to that one the results there are obsolete.
We are working to expose the new CIs results.
